VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.addJavascriptInterface\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:@JavascriptInterface|setAllowFileAccess\s*\(\s*false|setAllowUniversalAccessFromFileURLs\s*\(\s*false|trustedOrigin|allowlist
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects any call to addJavascriptInterface(), which exposes a native object to JavaScript running in a WebView.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for JavaScript Bridge Exposure: WebView.addJavascriptInterface().
